snippet.title: Snoop Dogg unveils "Fear & Respect" - Spike Video Game Awards 2004
snippet.description:
Snoop Dogg and John Singleton unveil their new video game with Midway called "Fear & Respect" at the Spike Video Game Awards on December 14th 2004. The trailer is shown off as well as some quick snippets of gameplay.

Sadly the game never came out, however this is the best footage of it out there.
